ies\",62\r\n108,AUTHOR,\"AUTHOR(\"\"ENTITY\"\"\",AUTHOR,61\r\n124,AUTHOR,AUTHORSHIP RESPONSIBILITY,\"Authors are accountable for the accuracy, integrity, and originality of their work, including the use of AI tools\",61\r\n133,AUTHOR,CODE CREATION,\"Authors may use AI tools for code creation, but must disclose this use and ensure the code's accuracy and originality\",61\r\n135,AUTHOR,ARTISTIC RENDERINGS,\"Authors may use AI tools to create artistic renderings, but must disclose this use and ensure the images' accuracy and originality\",61\r\n321,DISCLOSURE,POLICY,\"Policies require authors to disclose the use of AI tools in both the cover letter and the manuscript itselfPolicies require authors to disclose the use of AI tools in their work, including specific citations for AI-generated content\",61\r\n154,AUTHOR,APPENDIX,Authors may include detailed prompts used with LLMs in the online appendix of their manuscript,60\r\n106,AUTHOR,PAPERPAL PREFLIGHT,\"Authors may use Paperpal Preflight to improve spelling, grammar, and formatting without needing to disclose it\",60\r\n134,AUTHOR,CODE COPY-EDITING,\"Authors may use AI tools for code copy-editing, but must ensure the code's accuracy and originality\",60\r\n136,AUTHOR,EXPLANATORY DIAGRAMS,\"Authors may use AI tools to create explanatory diagrams, but must ensure the diagrams' accuracy and originality\",60\r\n137,AUTHOR,CONCEPTUAL FIGURE GENERATION,\"Authors may use AI tools to generate conceptual figures, but must ensure the figures' accuracy and originality\",60\r\n138,AUTHOR,TRANSLATION,\"Authors may use AI tools for translation, but must ensure the translated content's accuracy and originality\",60\r\n139,AUTHOR,CODE OF ETHICS,\"Authors must adhere to the code of ethics, which includes responsible and transparent use of AI tools\",60\r\n147,AUTHOR,\"MANUS(\"\"ENTITY\"\"\",IMAGE,60\r\n155,AUTHOR,PROMPT,Authors should document the exact prompts given to LLMs in the manuscript or online appendix,60\r\n156,AUTHOR,CITATI